Env.Var.mapt.Info.Value = Warning : You currently share an IPv4 with other subscriber. This is perfectly normal in a new IPv6 infrastructure. However, one of the consequences is that there is only a limited amount of external ports available to you. You can access this list by going to the external port input area in your settings, and press the <button class="btn" type="button"  style="outline: 0;"><i class="icon-th icon-white"></i></button> button. 
Env.Var.mapt.popup.Title.Value =  Mutual IPv4 public address port range
Env.Var.mapt.popup.Description.Value = Please find here the port range available to you, to help you define the port fowarding rules related to you public IPv4 address.
